Step By Step
~~~~~~~~~~~~
git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/vundle
cp .vimrc ~/.vimrc
open vim, run ":BundleInstall"
cp vim-autocomplpop.zip /usr/share/vim/vim73
unzip vim-autocomplpop.zip

Tips
~~~~
Find files:                  ctrl+p
Look up manual:              F2
generate tags:               F3
check php error:             F5
close atuo complete:         F6
open & close NERDTree:       F11
open & close Tagbar:         F12
how to use MiniBufExplorer:  ctrl+w,k
go to defination, jump back: ctrl+], ctrl+o



